name: Harvest Hoodie Maize
description:
This sleeveless v-neck hoodie has a large hood, with a front pocket.  Hood has an adjustable drawstring closure, with cowrie shells on the ends. Can be worn over a shirt with sleeves, or a tank.

Colors: Pale Yellow, Burnt Orange, and Mint Green.  Acrylic blend.
Size: Smedium (Small-Medium)

name: Harvest Hoodie Sky
description:
This sleeveless v-neck hoodie has a large hood, with a front pocket.  Hood has an adjustable drawstring closure, with the precious stone of Yellow Jade on the ends. Can be worn over a shirt with sleeves, or a tank.

Colors: Sky Blue, Turquoise, Burgundy, Pea Green, & Purple. Acrylic blend.
Size: Smedium (Small-Medium)

name: NiNi Sweater Halter
description:

Elastic band under the busts, along with an adjustable tie at the neck, provides a more personalized fit.

Size: Medium

name: Oshun Bound Scarf
description:
This fabric has a very cozy & soft touch.  Bound on each end with copper ribbon and rainbow metallic thread. The ends are also embellished with beads, a brass African ornament, and peacock feathers.  Acrylic & rayon.

Variegated hues of Reds, Orange, and Purple. 
One size.

description:

Variegated hues of Beige, Cream, and Copper. 
One size.

Colors: Blue, Turquoise, off White, Red, Pea Green, and Mustard.
One Size.

description:

description:
The Hausa Duffle is crocheted with yarn, and lined with an African print fabric. Edges and handles are crocheted with both yarn and African fabric.

Pea Green. Wool, Acrylic, & Rayon Blend.

name: Zaire Clutch
description:
Clutch purse is crocheted in a grey and multi colored yarn, and lined in purple fabric.  Magnetic snap closure.

Colors: Grey, & Multi. Purple lining.

name: Zaire Clutch Pink
description:

Colors: Pink & Chocolate Brown. Chocolate Brown lining.

name: Taqua Ruffle Hat
description:
Taqua ruffle hat is crocheted in lavender, with a purple boarder, and a multi-colored ruffle finish.  This hat can also be pulled down over the hair for a comfortable, snug fit.

Size: Medium. Acrylic blend.

name: Taqua Ruffle Warmers
description:
Taqua ruffle leg warmers are crocheted in lavender, with a purple boarder, and a multi-colored ruffle finish.  The very top is adorned with an adjustable draw string with copper bells, for a customized fit.  
Warmers can also be pushed further down the calf, for a more baggy look.  
Size: Medium. Acrylic blend.

name: Rwanda Smoke #1
description: Rwanda Smoke #1 is made from recycled incense boxes. Edges are crocheted leather. Paper on paper. Measures 10 inches around and approx. 2.5 inches across. Bracelet may have a faint aroma of incense.

name: Rwanda Blue
description:
Enjoy these rich colors of Cobalt Blue, Turquoise, and Gold. Cotton, suede, acrylic paint, and paper. 

This one is adjustable by way of an opening in the bottom to fit larger wrists. Measures 10 inches around, opening allows for more room. Approximately 2.5 inches across.

name: Rwanda Red
